{"type":null,"faqId":7632,"title":"WLAN经常中断，如何处理？","answer":"WLAN休眠策略里面永不休眠，实际上会休眠，造成中断。<br />设置-&gt;无线和网络-&gt;WLAN 设置-&gt;菜单键-&gt;高级-&gt;WLAN休眠策略<br />1、屏幕关闭时休眠：屏幕关闭15 分钟后进入休眠。<br />2、充电式永不休眠：只要是在充电状态下就不进入休眠。<br />3、永不休眠：一直不会进入休眠。","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7772","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1324546359000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":1027,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":45,"times":19,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":2.4,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}